OL,3,CBritish father-to-be feels like
OL,4,C'second class citizen' over family
OL,5,Cvisa rules
OL,7,FBut the couple are facing being split
OL,8,Fup for Mr Todd to return to the UK
OL,9,Falone to build up enough income proof
OL,10,Fas the British citizen in the
OL,11,Frelationship, or raise savings of more
OL,12,Fthan #88,500 dictated by the visa
OL,13,Frules to allow them to return as a
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FMr Todd told the PA news agency:
OL,17,F"There's been lots of times where I've
OL,18,Fstayed awake at night worrying about
OL,19,Fit and how it's all going to work out,
OL,20,Fbecause you feel completely helpless.
