OL,3,CBritish father-to-be feels like
OL,4,C'second class citizen' over family
OL,5,Cvisa rules
OL,7,FIt warned against raising the
OL,8,Fthreshold for family visas to the same
OL,9,Flevel for skilled workers, as planned
OL,10,Fby the previous government.
OL,12,FSkilled workers are only eligible to
OL,13,Fcome to the UK if they earn a salary
OL,14,Fof #38,700 or more, compared to
OL,15,F#29,000 required mainly for family
OL,16,Fvisas.
OL,18,FThe UK's current #29,000 threshold,
OL,19,Fwhich was set in 2024, is high
OL,20,Fcompared to other high-income
OL,21,Fcountries reviewed by the MAC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
