OL,7,FBritish father Ed Moon, currently
OL,8,Fliving in Taipei with his Taiwanese
OL,9,Fwife Amber Moon and four-year-old
OL,10,Fdaughter Maya, is also applying to the
OL,11,Ffamily visa route to move back to the
OL,12,FUK as Maya reaches school age.
OL,14,FHe told PA the most difficult thing is
OL,15,Fthe "extremely extensive"
OL,16,Fdocumentation you need to provide with
OL,17,Fany errors meaning the visa is denied
OL,18,Fand the process must be started again,
OL,19,Fwith visa fees costing around #2,000.
