OL,7,FThe journalist also said it is a waste
OL,8,Fof money for the taxpayer for him to
OL,9,Fgrow up and be educated in the UK, to
OL,10,Fthen not let him and his family live
OL,11,Fthere, adding: "I want to be able to
OL,12,Fcontribute to the UK."
OL,14,FThe research by Reunite Families and
OL,15,FCoram found that British citizens face
OL,16,Fexile, increased financial pressure
OL,17,Fand separation from their partners
OL,18,Foften for long periods of time from
OL,19,Fthe family visa policy.
