OL,7,FFor children separated from one of
OL,8,Ftheir parents, the charities warned
OL,9,Fthey can face life-changing trauma and
OL,10,Fdistress.
OL,12,FThe report also highlighted how the
OL,13,Frules particularly discriminate
OL,14,Fagainst those including British
OL,15,Fmothers, who are more likely to
OL,16,Fexperience hardship, working class and
OL,17,Flow income partners and black and
OL,18,Fethnic minority workers, who are more
OL,19,Flikely to earn less than their white
OL,20,Fcounterparts.
