OL,5,Cvisa rules
OL,7,FReunite Families UK executive director
OL,8,FCaroline Coombs said "simple and
OL,9,Fpractical changes" from the Home
OL,10,FOffice could make significant
OL,11,Fdifferences to families, starting with
OL,12,Fscrapping the MIR and simplifying the
OL,13,Frules and application process to stop
OL,14,Fthe need for expensive legal advice.
OL,16,F"These rules have become the tax on
OL,17,Flove. People are suffering and want to
OL,18,Fbe heard."
