OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Funderstand the minimum income
OL,9,Frequirement for family visas needs to
OL,10,Fbalance a respect for family life
OL,11,Fwhile also maintaining the UK's
OL,12,Feconomic stability, which is why the
OL,13,FHome Secretary commissioned the
OL,14,Findependent Migration Advisory
OL,15,FCommittee to undertake a review.
OL,17,F"We are now considering its findings
OL,18,Fand will respond in due course."
